T1  - A Relational Theory of Reputational Stability and Change
AU  - Zavyalova, Anastasiya
AU  - Bundy, Jonathan
AU  - Humphrey, Stephen E.
Y1  - 2021/09/16
PY  - 2021
DA  - 2022/09/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/orsc.2021.1494
