T1  - Detrimental Collaborations in Creative Work: Evidence from Economics
AU  - Vakili, Keyvan
AU  - Teodoridis, Florenta
AU  - Bikard, Michaël
Y1  - 2021/10/08
PY  - 2021
DA  - 2022/09/01
